Maxima's form disappeared in the river & swept far from the Ark. 

By the time she resurfaced, she was washed ashore miles & miles away. 

Laying upon the golden sand as the sun made her form shimmer, & the clear 
water washed upon her. Coming to, her crimson optics glowed, "Un-Mmmmm..." she 
attempted to sit up, but collapsed. Her back side was stiff as her pain sensors 
then registered, "Ahhh!" she groaned. However, she couldn't remember what 
happened. 

Sittin up on her elbows, her optics gazed at the area before her. Dazed & 
unsure what was going on... let alone where she was. 

Finally, slowly moving to her knees, the majority of her coms or beacons.. 
anything of the sort were damaged & unusable. Her meta processor however was so 
confused. She was wondering who she was, why she was here, what she was doing? 


Her optics looked over herself, noticing some damage. Including the metallic 
wings, they were ripped off & apart. 

Standing, then noticing the virgin land before her. It was beyond beautiful.  
Stumbling off the beach as she made her way onto the land before her. 

--part1_9f.3949db15.2c102890_boundary
